<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>FIR Draft</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        FIRST INFORMATION REPORT (FIR) DRAFT
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <p><strong>To:</strong><br>
        The Station House Officer<br>
        {{ police_station }}</p>
        
        <p><strong>Subject:</strong> Complaint for registration of FIR</p>
        
        <p>Sir,</p>
        
        <p>I, {{ complainant_name }}, resident of {{ complainant_address }}, hereby lodge this complaint for registration of FIR regarding the following incident:</p>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p><strong>Details of the Incident:</strong></p>
            <p><strong>Date of Incident:</strong> {{ incident_date }}</p>
            <p><strong>Time of Incident:</strong> {{ incident_time }}</p>
            <p><strong>Place of Incident:</strong> {{ incident_place }}</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p><strong>Details of Accused:</strong></p>
            <p><strong>Name:</strong> {{ accused_name }}</p>
            <p><strong>Address:</strong> {{ accused_address }}</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p><strong>Description of Incident:</strong></p>
            <p>{{ incident_description }}</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p><strong>Witnesses:</strong></p>
            <p>{{ witnesses }}</p>
        </div>
        
        <p>I request you to kindly register an FIR in this matter and take necessary legal action against the accused person(s). I am ready to cooperate in the investigation.</p>
        
        <p>I hereby declare that the above information is true to the best of my knowledge and belief.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="date-place">
        <p>Date: {{ date }}<br>
        Place: {{ place }}</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="signature">
        <p>Yours faithfully,<br><br>
        {{ complainant_name }}<br>
        Address: {{ complainant_address }}<br>
        Phone: {{ complainant_phone }}</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
